{"tid":613301,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"憨乜鳩野  係咪唔識寫個「戇」字","createTime":"2018-04-01T14:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T00:06:49.000Z","uid":17510,"like":138,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"1f071693578ebe772311b3133c12892f179b3fb2","tid":613301,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T14:35:46.000Z","msg":"憨<br />\n<a href=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%E9w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-can%2Fsearch.php%3Fq%3D%25E9w&d=QaYi2TILjXFrVXWM4cSVYgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=c6053f4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%E9w</a><br />\n音節: ham1<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戇<br />\n<a href=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%F9%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-can%2Fsearch.php%3Fq%3D%25F9%25BA&d=QaYi2TILjXFrVXWM4cSVYgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=61574d13\" target=\"_blank\">http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%F9%BA</a><br />\n音節: ngong6<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解而家咁多人分唔清依兩隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n台灣人online game用個憨字係多數用黎叫人做 「喜憨兒」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地香港人用個戇字，多數就用作戇居、戇鳩、戇豆先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解而家咁撚多人寫憨鳩   音又唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 憨乜撚野憨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42151d80894d575fa8abe013fddee70e6ba61c7b","tid":613301,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T14:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>66﹒﹛戇qong 3人，憨kam人﹜目前伴唱帶，常把「戇人」寫成「憨人」，大誤，須改進。台語界用法：<br />\n1戇人qonglang 32，真的笨人。<br />\n2憨人kamlang 12，外表憨厚，其實並不笨。如：祖母叫愛孫叫憨孫。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://blog.xuite.net/twgadang/twblog/137390411-台語漢字書寫法+++下集(3)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.xuite.net%2Ftwgadang%2Ftwblog%2F137390411-%E5%8F%B0%E8%AA%9E%E6%BC%A2%E5%AD%97%E6%9B%B8%E5%AF%AB%E6%B3%95%2B%2B%2B%E4%B8%8B%E9%9B%86%283%29&d=QaYi2TILjXFrVXWM4cSVYgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=d62041d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://blog.xuite.net/twgadang/twblog/137390411-台語漢字書寫法+++下集(3)</a>"},{"pid":"195feab0508e7cd2eed6fe74ea33baed7dc6bbed","tid":613301,"uid":17510,"like":83,"dislike":2,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T14:41:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戇</span><br />\n<br />\n放大啲比大家睇真啲隻字<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/223925_32a3058b436eb7678b935c2a252ee65b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F223925_32a3058b436eb7678b935c2a252ee65b.png&h=4241064b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小學無學過「戇直」依個詞語咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5ba6b419ea91f2f00f2117278acddd3ec306b0","tid":613301,"uid":68014,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T14:42:41.000Z","msg":"仲有「抄」「炒」<br />\n「抵」「低」「底」<br />\n成撚日見到d人講低死就想屌爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd904d685c0531e81d76efffbffb54a13382702","tid":613301,"uid":21423,"like":95,"dislike":2,"score":93,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T14:46:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9c6cbd53908f08dbc8bfa9fb6529c5a32dc19ac","tid":613301,"uid":17510,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"0cd904d685c0531e81d76efffbffb54a13382702","tid":613301,"uid":21423,"like":95,"dislike":2,"score":93,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T14:46:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T16:08:57.000Z","msg":"個憨字根本就唔同個戇字<br />\n讀音同意思都完全唔同<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解班傻仔話啱<img src=\"/assets/face